====================================

v. 0.2
====================================

Usability:
- support for local AJAX requests
- dependency scanner & script packer
- updated Bulgarian translation

Configuration:
- nice HTML configuration interface
- settings in JSON format
- configuration option to disable page reload from context menu
- configuration option to disable going to start page from context menu

Scripting:
- Perl interpreter check on browser start-up
- Perl interpreter from user PATH using: perl -e 'print $^X'
- custom environment variables in script environment
- compile-time settings printed as qDebug messages

GUI:
- working maximized window setting on Mac
